5th May !!!!! I’ve been waiting for you !! .
.
But...... @mcdsg announced further extension ! 我的天啊 ！ .
Again need to visualise my Big Macs 🍔 Nuggets, Apple pie 🥧 , Fries w/o salt 🍟 :( .

.
Together we can fight this virus together 💪🏻 .
Stay Home, Stay Safe and keep a lookout for McDonald’s more updates. .
I MISS YOU SO MUCH @mcdsg 💓 💕 .
